{"_id":"1OdEFpyyVOhLwx1T","name":"Scout","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Someone needs to find the way, to mark the route and lead others on. That's what you do. Every army needs you, the pathfinder, the scout. The spoor of many a beast is known to you, worse luck.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A rugged pony, camping gear and a small tent, dice for those quiet nights.</p>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerS