{"_id":"LJ7xdbzNmvyEmprx","name":"Merchant","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You've gone up in the world. No more hawking rubbish for you, you are a person of quality, a true trader, and people know it. You don't sell the things you trade, you talk about them. Others deal in the grubby business of selling.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: Burgher's clothes, a writ of trade, a wagon and a warehouse.</p>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{