{"_id":"PyCzhywq4KduBhNQ","name":"Mercenary Captain","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You're the Captain because you outlived the rest. Or maybe because you shout the loudest. Either way, people look up to you now. Not nice people, but people all the same.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A rough and ready sword, a battered suit of plate (heavy armour) and a baton of command.</p>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCar