{"_id":"PyN2VwmFD2vtLb5L","name":"Charlatan","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You are good at getting people to believe what you tell them, usually so that you can get them to buy what you sell them. Some consider you a criminal, but you don't - you're much more refined than that.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A suit of fine quality clothes, a tall fashionable hat, a discreet arming sword.</p>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"maxim