{"_id":"dQ2cWSJPvlTSo91F","name":"Wizard","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You've collected enough spells, and learnt enough of the otherworld, to call yourself a wizard. Now others tremble at your power. As long as you don't make a mistake casting your spells, the world is at your feet. Just don't make a mistake...</p>\n<p>Required equipment: At least five spells, numerous scraps of mystical writings and fake spells, a staff inset with a jewel to show others of your power.</p>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Command":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCar