{"_id":"jZ2yowL0CWo7bHNK","name":"Bravo","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You are a street fighter, flashy and grinning. You consider yourself a cut above the rest, but others see you just as a thug or assassin. More fool them. You're a king of the streets, strutting and brave, and you should be treated as such.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A fine arming sword, flashy clothes and a jaunty hat.</p>","activeSystem":"warlock","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"adventuringSkills":{"warlock":{"Appraise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Athletics":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Bargain":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Blunt":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Bow":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Brawling":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Command":{"maximumLevel":14,"isCareerSkill":true},"Crossbow":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Diplomacy":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Disguise":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Dodge":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Endurance":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"History":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Incantation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Intimidate":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Language":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Large blade":{"maximumLevel":16,"isCareerSkill":true},"Lie":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Medicine":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Navigation":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Ostler":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Persuasion":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Pole arm":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Repair":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Sleight of hand":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Small blade":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Spot":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Stealth":{"maximumLevel":0,"isCareerSkill":false},"Streetwise":{"